and other sites. I believe because VL may make some adjustments to account for
companies that have a reporting year that's not the same as a calendar year
(i.e. 12/31).

I used to occasionally read VL for its list of net-net or cash rich companies.
I haven't done that lately though.

I don't use VL rankings.

