Tempurpedic was not even in the running. I think it was ridiculously expensive.
We looked at other memory foam brands. Ultimately, we bought mattress from
IKEA, since we bought the bed there too. Have no clue how it compares to
Tempurpedic or others in terms of quality. I believe there is a lot of placebo
effects of people brainwashed that some brand/mattress is great saying that
it's great. But perhaps there are some real quantitative differences. Without
independent double blind study, I'd not take anyone's word for it. :)

